headline: Provident Healthcare Partners Advises Acentus in its Acquisition by Henry Schein
summary: Provident Healthcare Partners ("Provident"), a leading healthcare investment banking firm, announced it has advised Acentus in the acquisition of substantially all of its assets by Henry Schein, Inc. Acentus is a national medical supplier specializing in the delivery of Continuous Glucose Monitors (CGMs).
